# HTTP Client requests cho API Gateway mini-lab
#
# Điều kiện:
# - tenant-demo chạy ở http://localhost:8080.
# - gateway-demo chạy ở http://localhost:8081.
# - Token lấy từ auth-token-api.http hoặc private env.
#
# Không paste token thật vào Git.

@gateway_demo_base_url = http://localhost:8081
@invalid_token = invalid.jwt.token

### Gateway -> tenant-demo health route
# Expected: 200 nếu tenant-demo đang chạy.
GET {{gateway_demo_base_url}}/tenant-demo/actuator/health

### Gateway route: list master data with token
# Expected: 200 nếu token hợp lệ.
# Expected tenant-demo log có requestId=gateway-demo-001.
GET {{gateway_demo_base_url}}/api/master-data
X-Request-Id: gateway-demo-001
Authorization: Bearer {{tenant1_token}}

### Gateway route: missing token
# Expected: 401 từ tenant-demo, không phải business logic trong gateway.
GET {{gateway_demo_base_url}}/api/master-data
X-Request-Id: gateway-missing-token-001

### Gateway route: invalid token
# Expected: 401 từ tenant-demo.
GET {{gateway_demo_base_url}}/api/master-data
X-Request-Id: gateway-invalid-token-001
Authorization: Bearer {{invalid_token}}

### Query by code through gateway
# Expected: vẫn scoped theo tenant từ token.
GET {{gateway_demo_base_url}}/api/master-data/code/LAPTOP-01
X-Request-Id: gateway-code-001
Authorization: Bearer {{tenant1_token}}

### Gateway app own health
# Expected: 200 nếu gateway-demo đang chạy.
GET {{gateway_demo_base_url}}/actuator/health
